{"type":"message","id":"6a3d437b","parentId":"27fd80b1","timestamp":"2026-05-28T07:17:30.395Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Good — no stuck cron jobs or zombie sessions. Here's the breakdown:\n\n**Cron Jobs: ✅ All Clear**\n- **Auto-update FreeRide + Aider** — Running fine, last ran successfully yesterday at 6am. Next run today at 6am.\n- **Sessions Cleanup** — Disabled (was never needed after all)\n- **Session Auto-Expiry** — Disabled\n- **Daily Station Check** — Disabled, last run timed out (it was doing too much — shell-only job but with a massive prompt). Not stuck, just off.\n\n**Sessions: ✅ All Clear**\n- Only one active session — this one (our Telegram chat). No zombie sub-agents or stale sessions hanging around.\n\nNow let me get context on the Mission Control review you were asking about. Let me check yesterday's conversation and the task file."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"df2f04aa-610e-4801-a4b2-47849b56b03f","name":"memory_search","arguments":{"query":"Mission Control review recommendations subagents tools test"},"partialArgs":"{\"query\": \"Mission Control review recommendations subagents tools test\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"11c79543-8cea-4d14-9b1a-ed308f5fdfb2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat ~/.openclaw/workspace/data/tasks.json 2>/dev/null || echo \"NO TASKS FILE\""},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"cat ~/.openclaw/workspace/data/tasks.json 2>/dev/null || echo \\\"NO TASKS FILE\\\"\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/owl-alpha","usage":{"input":11189,"output":237,"cacheRead":9344,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20770,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779952636341,"responseId":"gen-1779952636-wXj4vqpKOrSfuHWnbIE7"}}
{"type":"message","id":"a4dea0f5","parentId":"6a3d437b","timestamp":"2026-05-28T07:17:30.483Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"df2f04aa-610e-4801-a4b2-47849b56b03f","toolName":"memory_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"dd2e01115246e4a65c12b70143821cb0fbdd8cc835177c77b94ae200623906b3\",\n      \"path\": \"MEMORY.md\",\n      \"startLine\": 1,\n      \"endLine\": 26,\n      \"score\": 1,\n      \"textScore\": 0.6294816329885456,\n      \"snippet\": \"# MEMORY.md — Long-Term Memory\\n\\n_Curated memory. Distilled from daily logs and the wiki. Only the essentials._\\n\\n## The Wiki\\n\\nI now maintain a **Karpathy-style LLM Wiki** at `memory/wiki/`. This is my primary knowledge management system — a structured, interlinked collection of markdown pages that compounds over time.\\n\\n- **Index:** `memory/wiki/index.md` — content catalog of all pages\\n- **Overview:** `memory/wiki/overview.md` — high-level synthesis\\n- **Log:** `memory/wiki/log.md` — chronological activity record\\n- **Schema:** `memory/wiki/schema.md` — conventions and workflows\\n- **Entities:** `memory/wiki/entities/` — people, projects, tools\\n- **Concepts:** `memory/wiki/concepts/` — ideas, pat\\n\\nSource: MEMORY.md#L1-L26\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"citation\": \"MEMORY.md#L1-L26\",\n      \"corpus\": \"memory\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"8c2a159a5ef795ba7c3ffd28c1abf31e38f6588ef79afc3246cb296105e93cc9\",\n      \"path\": \"memory/2026-05-16.md\",\n      \"startLine\": 15,\n      \"endLine\": 41,\n      \"score\": 1,\n      \"textScore\": 0.722205073274348,\n      \"snippet\": \"- **CANCELLED** — Andre decided against it. OpenClaw data is only 1.2 GB, not worth the complexity. Andre will use an external SSD instead.\\n- Disk cleanup also cancelled — no action needed.\\n# 2026-05-16 — Daily Log\\n\\n## Morning Session\\n\\n### Completed\\n- **Station Uptime Indicator** — Added Ship's Chronometer to Spacestation page + Dashboard\\n- **Disk Space Widget** — Added to Spacestation + Dashboard\\n- **Restart Mission Control Button** — New Quick Action in Dashboard\\n- **Awaiting Review Badge** — Sidebar Tasks icon shows yellow badge with count\\n- **Daily Telegram Sitrep** — Updated 23:00 cron job\\n- **Server Data Extensions** — Added gatewayUptime, wdDisk stats, new server functions\\n- **Build +\\n\\nSource: memory/2026-05-16.md#L15-L41\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"citation\": \"memory/2026-05-16.md#L15-L41\",\n      \"corpus\": \"memory\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"fe8b7368b0b678e2b599f372b6dd243a082578469b74c5825b693042aecbba4d\",\n      \"path\": \"memory/mission-control-plan.md\",\n      \"startLine\": 1,\n      \"endLine\": 35,\n      \"score\": 1,\n      \"textScore\": 0.1919783884791993,\n      \"snippet\": \"# Systems Engineer Brief: Wire Mission Control to Real Data\\n\\n## Input\\n- Dashboard project from Lovable at: ~/Downloads/mission-control.zip\\n- OpenClaw workspace at: ~/.openclaw/workspace/\\n\\n## Steps\\n\\n### 1. Unzip\\n- Extract ~/Downloads/mission-control.zip to ~/mission-control-dashboard\\n- If unzip hangs, use Python: python3 -c \\\"import zipfile; zipfile.ZipFile('~/Downloads/mission-control.zip').extractall('~/mission-control-dashboard')\\\"\\n\\n### 2. Explore Project Structure\\n- Read package.json (stack, deps, scripts)\\n- Map src/routes/, src/lib/, src/components/\\n- Identify every file containing mock/sample data\\n- Read routing setup to understand current navigation\\n- Note: project may be TanStack Start\\n\\nSource: memory/mission-control-plan.md#L1-L35\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"citation\": \"memory/mission-control-plan.md#L1-L35\",\n      \"corpus\": \"memory\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"6e0c89ec9fd6924702d448bad39add950517b0e6317277eae7c785edfa4b5847\",\n      \"path\": \"memory/proposed-cron-jobs.md\",\n      \"startLine\": 1,\n      \"endLine\": 47,\n      \"score\": 1,\n      \"textScore\": 0.7205341533760095,\n      \"snippet\": \"# Proposed Cron Jobs for Mission Control\\n# All created as DISABLED for review before enabling\\n\\n## Existing (already created)\\n1. Work Dispatcher — every 15 min — DISABLED (was erroring on Telegram delivery)\\n2. OpenClaw Daily Backup — daily 3 AM — exists but erroring\\n\\n## Proposed (to create, all disabled)\\n\\n3. Log Rotation — weekly Sunday 2 AM\\n   - Rotate and compress logs older than 7 days\\n   - Archive to WD MyCloud\\n\\n4. Storage Health Check — daily 6 AM\\n   - Check local disk usage\\n   - Check WD MyCloud availability\\n   - Alert if disk >80% or WD MyCloud unreachable\\n\\n5. Task Queue Cleanup — daily midnight\\n   - Archive completed tasks older than 30 days\\n   - Move to data/tasks-archive.json\\n\\n6. Wi\\n\\nSource: memory/proposed-cron-jobs.md#L1-L47\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"citation\": \"memory/proposed-cron-jobs.md#L1-L47\",\n      \"corpus\": \"memory\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"137947943bba9845a0b9473e8c0a9f26eb4a95a114f043e08575dc402e89f6fa\",\n      \"path\": \"memory/wiki/plan.md\",\n      \"startLine\": 26,\n      \"endLine\": 66,\n      \"score\": 1,\n      \"textScore\": 0.6361845707499015,\n      \"snippet\": \"│       ├── overview.md        # High-level synthesis of everything in the wiki\\n│       ├── entities/          # Entity pages (people, projects, tools, concepts)\\n│       │   ├── andre.md\\n│       │   ├── space-monkey.md\\n│       │   ├── mission-control.md\\n│       │   └── openclaw.md\\n│       ├── concepts/          # Concept/thematic pages\\n│       │   ├── agent-memory.md\\n│       │   ├── mission-control-dashboard.md\\n│       │   └── llm-wiki-pattern.md\\n│       ├── sources/           # Summaries of ingested source documents\\n│       │   └── karpathy-llm-wiki-gist.md\\n│       └── comparisons/       # Comparison tables, analyses, slide decks\\n│           └── (future)\\n└── raw/                       # Raw\\n\\nSource: memory/wiki/plan.md#L26-L66\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"citation\": \"memory/wiki/plan.md#L26-L66\",\n      \"corpus\": \"memory\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"bf3561139356b08cd8628bb65561f0a0b800206f557df7971e4bc61cd1563cd6\",\n      \"path\": \"memory/wiki/plan.md\",\n      \"startLine\": 1,\n      \"endLine\": 32,\n      \"score\": 1,\n      \"textScore\": 0.6264353781670395,\n      \"snippet\": \"# Karpathy LLM Wiki — Implementation Plan for OpenClaw\\n\\n## Goal\\n\\nTransform my flat, append-only memory files into a persistent, compounding knowledge wiki — a structured, interlinked collection of markdown pages that grows richer with every interaction, ingest, and query.\\n\\n## Current State\\n\\n- `MEMORY.md` — exists but empty (no curated long-term memory yet)\\n- `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md` — daily raw logs (only one: 2026-05-11.md)\\n- `memory/mission-control-plan.md` — a project plan, not really memory\\n- No structure, no cross-references, no entity pages, no index, no log\\n- Memory is essentially a flat diary — I rediscover everything from scratch each session\\n\\n## Target Architecture\\n\\n```\\n~/.openclaw/w\\n\\nSource: memory/wiki/plan.md#L1-L32\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"citation\": \"memory/wiki/plan.md#L1-L32\",\n      \"corpus\": \"memory\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"provider\": \"none\",\n  \"citations\": \"auto\",\n  \"debug\": {\n    \"backend\": \"builtin\",\n    \"effectiveMode\": \"n/a\",\n    \"searchMs\": 47,\n    \"hits\": 6\n  }\n}"}],"details":{"results":[{"id":"dd2e01115246e4a65c12b70143821cb0fbdd8cc835177c77b94ae200623906b3","path":"MEMORY.md","startLine":1,"endLine":26,"score":1,"textScore":0.6294816329885456,"snippet":"# MEMORY.md — Long-Term Memory\n\n_Curated memory. Distilled from daily logs and the wiki. Only the essentials._\n\n## The Wiki\n\nI now maintain a **Karpathy-style LLM Wiki** at `memory/wiki/`. This is my primary knowledge management system — a structured, interlinked collection of markdown pages that compounds over