{"type":"message","id":"5225d4f8","parentId":"c2f791b2","timestamp":"2026-05-28T09:05:29.148Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**200!** Server is running and responding. Now let me fix the API route warnings by adding the ignore pattern to vite config:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"b0db8420-ea79-4de2-9e12-7e66dd7ed39b","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/spacemonkey/.openclaw/workspace/mission-control-dashboard/vite.config.ts"},"partialArgs":"{\"path\": \"/Users/spacemonkey/.openclaw/workspace/mission-control-dashboard/vite.config.ts\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/owl-alpha","usage":{"input":724,"output":61,"cacheRead":78592,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":79377,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779959108138,"responseId":"gen-1779959108-WDdtiWiu5hX3HDuCdEIB"}}
{"type":"message","id":"524d4e15","parentId":"5225d4f8","timestamp":"2026-05-28T09:05:29.308Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"b0db8420-ea79-4de2-9e12-7e66dd7ed39b","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"// @lovable.dev/vite-tanstack-config already includes the following — do NOT add them manually\n// or the app will break with duplicate plugins:\n//   - tanstackStart, viteReact, tailwindcss, tsConfigPaths, cloudflare (build-only),\n//     componentTagger (dev-only), VITE_* env injection, @ path alias, React/TanStack dedupe,\n//     error logger plugins, and sandbox detection (port/host/strictPort).\n// You can pass additional config via defineConfig({ vite: { ... } }) if needed.\nimport { defineConfig } from \"@lovable.dev/vite-tanstack-config\";\n\n// Redirect TanStack Start's bundled server entry to src/server.ts (our SSR error wrapper).\n// @cloudflare/vite-plugin builds from this — wrangler.jsonc main alone is insufficient.\nexport default defineConfig({\n  tanstackStart: {\n    server: { entry: \"server\" },\n  },\n  vite: {\n    server: {\n      headers: {\n        \"Cache-Control\": \"no-store, no-cache, must-revalidate, max-age=0\",\n      },\n      watch: {\n        usePolling: true,\n        interval: 500,\n      },\n    },\n  },\n});\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1779959129308}}
{"type":"message","id":"5f92ad77","parentId":"524d4e15","timestamp":"2026-05-28T09:05:52.402Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The API route warnings are from TanStart v8 being stricter. The proper fix is to add `routeFileIgnorePattern` to the TanStack Start config. But since this config is managed by `@lovable.dev/vite-tanstack-config`, let me check if I can add it:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"dd98092d-8296-45eb-9f79-3817e4971869","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/Users/spacemonkey/.openclaw/workspace/mission-control-dashboard/vite.config.ts","edits":[{"oldText":"export default defineConfig({\n  tanstackStart: {\n    server: { entry: \"server\" },\n  },","newText":"export default defineConfig({\n  tanstackStart: {\n    server: { entry: \"server\" },\n    routeFileIgnorePattern: \"-api-\" ,\n  },"}]},"partialArgs":"{\"path\": \"/Users/spacemonkey/.openclaw/workspace/mission-control-dashboard/vite.config.ts\", \"edits\": [{\"oldText\": \"export default defineConfig({\\n  tanstackStart: {\\n    server: { entry: \\\"server\\\" },\\n  },\", \"newText\": \"export default defineConfig({\\n  tanstackStart: {\\n    server: { entry: \\\"server\\\" },\\n    routeFileIgnorePattern: \\\"-api-\\\" ,\\n  },\"}]}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/owl-alpha","usage":{"input":417,"output":180,"cacheRead":79232,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":79829,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779959129310,"responseId":"gen-1779959129-3ioMpbmvsd8DYLEafyDa"}}
