{"type":"message","id":"b99c0286","parentId":"51dee207","timestamp":"2026-05-28T09:13:15.939Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Server is up and managed by LaunchAgent. Let me now update the daily log:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"8f4553ce-f52f-4939-a982-6bd72d8ec559","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/Users/spacemonkey/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-05-28.md","content":"# 2026-05-28 — Daily Log\n\n## Morning Session\n\n### Infrastructure\n- **Vite dev server down** — port 3000 not responding. LaunchAgent had died (exit code 143/SIGTERM, TimeMachine permission error).\n- **Fixed start-mc.sh** — was using `sed -i ''` to modify build-info.ts in-place on every start (corrupting git state). Now uses `VITE_*` env vars instead.\n- **OpenClaw updated** — 2026.5.20 → 2026.5.26\n- **LaunchAgent reloaded** with ThrottleInterval increased to 10→30s\n- **routeTree.gen.ts** added to .gitignore\n\n### Code Review — All Recommendations Implemented\n1. ✅ Removed `/home` test route (leftover duplicate)\n2. ✅ Cleaned up `sprites-old/` (12 files, 1.4MB)\n3. ✅ Renamed `calendar.tsx` → `scheduler.tsx` (matches sidebar label)\n4. ✅ Added \"Agent Office\" nav item to sidebar; `/spacestation` redirects to `/visual`\n5. ✅ Made index page dynamic — uses `getAgentStatus()` instead of hardcoded agents\n6. ✅ Added atomic write + in-memory lock to save-tasks API\n7. ✅ Added atomic write to `saveTasks` server function in server-data.ts\n8. ✅ Migrated build-info.ts from hardcoded values to `import.meta.env.VITE_*`\n9. ✅ Renamed all API route files from `.tsx` to `.ts`\n10. ✅ Added warning header to RoomCanvas.tsx (hand-tuned pixel art, don't auto-refactor)\n\n### Remaining Cosmetic Issues (not critical)\n- API route files show \"does not export a Route\" warnings in Vite dev mode (TanStack Start v8 cosmetic warnings — they work fine, just noisy)\n\n### Git\n- Committed and pushed all changes (commit: 21ea161)\n"},"partialArgs":"{\"path\": \"/Users/spacemonkey/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-05-28.md\", \"content\": \"# 2026-05-28 — Daily Log\\n\\n## Morning Session\\n\\n### Infrastructure\\n- **Vite dev server down** — port 3000 not responding. LaunchAgent had died (exit code 143/SIGTERM, TimeMachine permission error).\\n- **Fixed start-mc.sh** — was using `sed -i ''` to modify build-info.ts in-place on every start (corrupting git state). Now uses `VITE_*` env vars instead.\\n- **OpenClaw updated** — 2026.5.20 → 2026.5.26\\n- **LaunchAgent reloaded** with ThrottleInterval increased to 10→30s\\n- **routeTree.gen.ts** added to .gitignore\\n\\n### Code Review — All Recommendations Implemented\\n1. ✅ Removed `/home` test route (leftover duplicate)\\n2. ✅ Cleaned up `sprites-old/` (12 files, 1.4MB)\\n3. ✅ Renamed `calendar.tsx` → `scheduler.tsx` (matches sidebar label)\\n4. ✅ Added \\\"Agent Office\\\" nav item to sidebar; `/spacestation` redirects to `/visual`\\n5. ✅ Made index page dynamic — uses `getAgentStatus()` instead of hardcoded agents\\n6. ✅ Added atomic write + in-memory lock to save-tasks API\\n7. ✅ Added atomic write to `saveTasks` server function in server-data.ts\\n8. ✅ Migrated build-info.ts from hardcoded values to `import.meta.env.VITE_*`\\n9. ✅ Renamed all API route files from `.tsx` to `.ts`\\n10. ✅ Added warning header to RoomCanvas.tsx (hand-tuned pixel art, don't auto-refactor)\\n\\n### Remaining Cosmetic Issues (not critical)\\n- API route files show \\\"does not export a Route\\\" warnings in Vite dev mode (TanStack Start v8 cosmetic warnings — they work fine, just noisy)\\n\\n### Git\\n- Committed and pushed all changes (commit: 21ea161)\\n\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/owl-alpha","usage":{"input":86,"output":518,"cacheRead":86144,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":86748,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779959556178,"responseId":"gen-1779959556-YfCOa6HqHrBKUl8iLEhR"}}
