{"type":"message","id":"349ea639","parentId":"17a10e7f","timestamp":"2026-05-28T09:14:38.777Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"All done. Here's the full summary of everything that was done:\n\n---\n\n## ✅ All Recommendations Completed\n\n### Infrastructure & Stability\n1. **Vite dev server back up** — was down due to LaunchAgent crash. Fixed, reloaded, and now managed by LaunchAgent with KeepAlive\n2. **Updated OpenClaw** — 2026.5.20 → 2026.5.26\n3. **Fixed start-mc.sh** — no longer corrupts build-info.ts with `sed`; uses Vite env vars instead\n\n### Code Quality & Architecture\n4. **Removed `/home` test route** — was a leftover duplicate of Dashboard\n5. **Cleaned `sprites-old/`** — 12 old sprite files (1.4MB) removed\n6. **Renamed `calendar.tsx` → `scheduler.tsx`** — matches the \"Scheduler\" sidebar label\n7. **Added \"Agent Office\" to sidebar** — was missing from navigation entirely\n8. **Redirect `/spacestation` → `/visual`** — spacestation was a legacy duplicate of Agent Office\n9. **Dynamic index page** — now uses `getAgentStatus()` for real agent data instead of hardcoded values\n10. **Atomic file writes + locking** for `save-tasks` and `saveTasks` — prevents race conditions\n\n### Developer Experience\n11. **API routes `.tsx` → `.ts`** — proper file extensions\n12. **`routeTree.gen.ts` in .gitignore** — auto-generated file shouldn't be tracked\n13. **RoomCanvas warning header** — hand-tuned pixel art marked as fragile\n\nAll committed (21ea161) and pushed to both repos."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/owl-alpha","usage":{"input":285,"output":385,"cacheRead":87040,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":87710,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779959642051,"responseId":"gen-1779959642-6rE7j4zOVdEnNEoWfKWp"}}
