n- `server-data/quick-actions.ts`\n\n**5. Error boundary shows raw `error.message` to users**\nThe `ErrorComponent` in `__root.tsx` doesn't show the error message to users (good), BUT it only uses generic text. Consider adding an error ID + timestamp for supportability.\n\n**6. The `projects.json` file is tiny (956 bytes) and data is likely stale**\nCheck if the Projects page still works meaningfully or if it's dead content.\n\n**7. Scheduler page is 559 lines — too big**\nSplit the cron error table, job list, and controls into sub-components.\n\n### 🟢 Nice to Have\n\n**8. `task-flow-signals.tsx` is 41 lines but imported nowhere**\n`TaskFlowSignals.tsx` — check if this dead code can be removed.\n\n**9. Accessibility: add `aria-label`s to sidebar nav items**\nThe sidebar links have good visual styling but minimal screen-reader support.\n\n**10. Memory page has no content**\nBackfill a few daily logs from session transcripts, or import the wiki content into daily log format so the Memory page is useful.\n\n**11. Consider dark/light theme toggle**\nCurrently hardcoded to `class=\"dark\"` on `<html>`. The OKLCH color system could support both.\n\n---\n\nWant me to do these too? I'd suggest the **hardcoded version string (#1)**, **empty activity feed (#2)**, and **slow down the 15s invalidation (#3)** first since those are the most impactful. The file splits (#4, #7) are pure refactoring."}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openclaw","model":"delivery-mirror","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"total":0,"prompt_tokens":0,"completion_tokens":0,"total_tokens":0,"cache":{"read":0,"write":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779961215087}}
