{"type":"message","id":"63b1cdd9","parentId":"27340526","timestamp":"2026-05-28T11:06:12.141Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"83abae7c-d6fe-47d7-b298-f100a2f226fa","toolName":"memory_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"e65b53f79ad6cd55c8cc8a9750fa14e89aecafa5ced34aca3db15a637774b552\",\n      \"path\": \"memory/2026-05-12.md\",\n      \"startLine\": 1,\n      \"endLine\": 32,\n      \"score\": 1,\n      \"textScore\": 0.7575261895559219,\n      \"snippet\": \"# 2026-05-12\\n\\n## Karpathy LLM Wiki — Bootstrapped\\n- Created full wiki structure at `memory/wiki/` based on Karpathy's pattern\\n- 13 wiki files: schema, index, log, overview, 4 entities, 3 concepts, 1 source\\n- Updated MEMORY.md and AGENTS.md with wiki references\\n\\n## Backup System — Operational\\n- WD MyCloud mounted at `/Volumes/OpenClaw-WD` (guest access, Public share)\\n- Created 4 backup scripts + RECOVERY_GUIDE.md + BACKUP_GUIDE.md\\n- First full backup completed: 1.6MB\\n- Cron job configured: daily backup at 3:00 AM\\n\\n## Mission Control Dashboard — Full Build\\n- Moved to `~/mission-control-dashboard/`, bun installed, 494 deps\\n- 10 pages: Tasks, Calendar, Projects, Memory, Docs, Team, Visual, Incid\\n\\nSource: memory/2026-05-12.md#L1-L32\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"citation\": \"memory/2026-05-12.md#L1-L32\",\n      \"corpus\": \"memory\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"fe8b7368b0b678e2b599f372b6dd243a082578469b74c5825b693042aecbba4d\",\n      \"path\": \"memory/mission-control-plan.md\",\n      \"startLine\": 1,\n      \"endLine\": 35,\n      \"score\": 1,\n      \"textScore\": 0.2450948545844655,\n      \"snippet\": \"# Systems Engineer Brief: Wire Mission Control to Real Data\\n\\n## Input\\n- Dashboard project from Lovable at: ~/Downloads/mission-control.zip\\n- OpenClaw workspace at: ~/.openclaw/workspace/\\n\\n## Steps\\n\\n### 1. Unzip\\n- Extract ~/Downloads/mission-control.zip to ~/mission-control-dashboard\\n- If unzip hangs, use Python: python3 -c \\\"import zipfile; zipfile.ZipFile('~/Downloads/mission-control.zip').extractall('~/mission-control-dashboard')\\\"\\n\\n### 2. Explore Project Structure\\n- Read package.json (stack, deps, scripts)\\n- Map src/routes/, src/lib/, src/components/\\n- Identify every file containing mock/sample data\\n- Read routing setup to understand current navigation\\n- Note: project may be TanStack Start\\n\\nSource: memory/mission-control-plan.md#L1-L35\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"citation\": \"memory/mission-control-plan.md#L1-L35\",\n      \"corpus\": \"memory\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"e75b25c424c36397ad9a8c387eaba94db772296c21a9ce5081963d71f3f335db\",\n      \"path\": \"memory/wiki/entities/mission-control.md\",\n      \"startLine\": 28,\n      \"endLine\": 52,\n      \"score\": 1,\n      \"textScore\": 0.23109677558265443,\n      \"snippet\": \"- 2026-05-11 — ZIP extraction failed repeatedly\\n- 2026-05-12 — Andre said to leave it for tomorrow; plan stored in memory\\n\\n## Sources\\n- [[mission-control-dashboard]] — Concept page with full architecture\\n- memory/mission-control-plan.md — Detailed implementation plan\\n\\n## Open Questions\\n- How to fix ZIP extraction (try Python zipfile module?)\\n- Should we use bun or npm?\\n- When will Andre return to this project?\\n\\n## Dashboard Wired (2026-05-12)\\n- Moved from Downloads to `~/mission-control-dashboard/`\\n- Installed bun + 494 dependencies\\n- Replaced all mock data with live OpenClaw data via `createServerFn`\\n- Data sources: tasks.json, openclaw.json (cron), memory/*.md, MEMORY.md, workspace/*.md, p\\n\\nSource: memory/wiki/entities/mission-control.md#L28-L52\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"citation\": \"memory/wiki/entities/mission-control.md#L28-L52\",\n      \"corpus\": \"memory\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"63d1d35925d9e42c0625f69c48bfaac7c6fa803c08419fa0f24af898ae6bec04\",\n      \"path\": \"memory/wiki/entities/mission-control.md\",\n      \"startLine\": 1,\n      \"endLine\": 36,\n      \"score\": 1,\n      \"textScore\": 0.22853548505039817,\n      \"snippet\": \"# Mission Control\\n\\n**Type:** Project\\n**Status:** In Progress (blocked)\\n**First mentioned:** 2026-05-11\\n\\n## Summary\\n\\nA 7-screen dashboard app for monitoring the OpenClaw agent station. Built via Loveable as a TanStack Start app, designed with dark theme (#12182A), purple/green accents, pixel art avatars, and a left sidebar navigation. Currently blocked on ZIP extraction.\\n\\n## Key Facts\\n- **Stack:** TanStack Start (React-based, serverless edge → needs Node server for local fs)\\n- **Screens:** Tasks, Calendar, Projects, Memory, Docs, Team, Visual Office\\n- **Theme:** Dark (#12182A), purple/violet accents, lime green active states\\n- **Crew:** Space Monkey (Director), Life Support Officer, Systems E\\n\\nSource: memory/wiki/entities/mission-control.md#L1-L36\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"citation\": \"memory/wiki/entities/mission-control.md#L1-L36\",\n      \"corpus\": \"memory\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"0950eb233df147b25df2300603d673d5829892e78d21e318f6f5f1513911f328\",\n      \"path\": \"memory/wiki/log.md\",\n      \"startLine\": 1,\n      \"endLine\": 18,\n      \"score\": 1,\n      \"textScore\": 0.7631207650355857,\n      \"snippet\": \"# Wiki Log — Chronological Activity Record\\n\\n_Append-only timeline of what happened and when._\\n\\n## [2026-05-21] docs | SOURCES.md framework created\\n- Created `SOURCES.md` — canonical documentation authority with 19 verified Context7 sources across 5 tiers\\n- Created `FRAMEWORK.md` — framework selection guide with anti-patterns\\n- Updated `AGENTS.md` — added Source Selection Rules (5 rules: detect stack, load only relevant, separate architecture, follow priority, ask when in doubt)\\n- Fixed 8 broken Context7 links (original paths returned 404, found correct `/websites/` and org-prefixed paths)\\n- Full compatibility matrix: safe combinations + 8 forbidden combinations\\n- Project type → sources looku\\n\\nSource: memory/wiki/log.md#L1-L18\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"citation\": \"memory/wiki/log.md#L1-L18\",\n      \"corpus\": \"memory\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"4cee391387785d99b0bb20b954ab6737daf5ad116fa789b77bdb25c70f0d8b75\",\n      \"path\": \"memory/wiki/overview.md\",\n      \"startLine\": 25,\n      \"endLine\": 43,\n      \"score\": 1,\n      \"textScore\": 0.4363679834297721,\n      \"snippet\": \"- [[agent-memory]] — My memory architecture (daily logs + MEMORY.md + wiki)\\n- [[mission-control-dashboard]] — The dashboard project architecture\\n\\n## Open Questions\\n- When will the Mission Control ZIP extraction be unblocked?\\n- What sources should we ingest first beyond the Karpathy gist?\\n- Should we add a search tool (qmd) for the wiki, or is the index sufficient for now?\\n- Can we get write access to the WD MyCloud for off-site backup replication?\\n\\n## Health\\n- Pages: 10 (4 entities, 3 concepts, 1 source, 1 overview, 1 index)\\n- Orphans: 0 (all pages linked from index)\\n- Contradictions: 0\\n- Stale claims: 0\\n- Last lint: 2026-05-12 (bootstrap)\\n\\n---\\n*Last Updated: 2026-05-12 by Space Monkey*\\n\\nSource: memory/wiki/overview.md#L25-L43\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"citation\": \"memory/wiki/overview.md#L25-L43\",\n      \"corpus\": \"memory\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"provider\": \"none\",\n  \"citations\": \"auto\",\n  \"debug\": {\n    \"backend\": \"builtin\",\n    \"effectiveMode\": \"n/a\",\n    \"searchMs\": 64,\n    \"hits\": 6\n  }\n}"}],"details":{"results":[{"id":"e65b53f79ad6cd55c8cc8a9750fa14e89aecafa5ced34aca3db15a637774b552","path":"memory/2026-05-12.md","startLine":1,"endLine":32,"score":1,"textScore":0.7575261895559219,"snippet":"# 2026-05-12\n\n## Karpathy LLM Wiki — Bootstrapped\n- Created full wiki structure at `memory/wiki/` based on Karpathy's pattern\n- 13 wiki files: schema, index, log, overview, 4 entities, 3 