{"type":"message","id":"690ce3d8","parentId":"b8ab218c","timestamp":"2026-05-28T11:42:20.942Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The API route warnings are from TanStart v8 being stricter. The proper fix is to add `routeFileIgnorePattern` to the TanStack Start config. But since this config is managed by `@lovable.dev/vite-tanstack-config`, let me check if I can add it:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"dd98092d-8296-45eb-9f79-3817e4971869","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/Users/spacemonkey/.openclaw/workspace/mission-control-dashboard/vite.config.ts","edits":[{"oldText":"export default defineConfig({\n  tanstackStart: {\n    server: { entry: \"server\" },\n  },","newText":"export default defineConfig({\n  tanstackStart: {\n    server: { entry: \"server\" },\n    routeFileIgnorePattern: \"-api-\" ,\n  },"}]},"partialArgs":"{\"path\": \"/Users/spacemonkey/.openclaw/workspace/mission-control-dashboard/vite.config.ts\", \"edits\": [{\"oldText\": \"export default defineConfig({\\n  tanstackStart: {\\n    server: { entry: \\\"server\\\" },\\n  },\", \"newText\": \"export default defineConfig({\\n  tanstackStart: {\\n    server: { entry: \\\"server\\\" },\\n    routeFileIgnorePattern: \\\"-api-\\\" ,\\n  },\"}]}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/owl-alpha","usage":{"input":417,"output":180,"cacheRead":79232,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":79829,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779959129310,"responseId":"gen-1779959129-3ioMpbmvsd8DYLEafyDa"}}
