{"type":"message","id":"05ca1a1a","parentId":"875e3da0","timestamp":"2026-05-28T11:42:20.949Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\nLet me give you a clear picture of where things stand and what's left.\n\n## ✅ Completed (both rounds)\n\n**Round 1 (11 items):**\n- Removed `/home` test route, cleaned up `sprites-old/` (1.4MB)\n- Renamed `calendar.tsx` → `scheduler.tsx`\n- Added \"Agent Office\" to sidebar, redirected `/spacestation` → `/visual`\n- Made index page dynamic with real agent status\n- Atomic writes + locking for task saves\n- Fixed `start-mc.sh` (no more `sed` corruption)\n- Updated OpenClaw to latest (2026.5.26)\n\n**Round 2 (10 items):**\n- Split `server-data.ts` (1037 lines) → 14 domain modules\n- Activity feed now shows real tasks, incidents, cron errors\n- Router invalidation 15s → 60s\n- Added aria-labels to sidebar nav\n- Removed dead `memory-data.ts`\n- Fixed hardcoded `openclawVersion`\n- All TypeScript compiles clean, all routes 200\n\n## ⏭️ What's left from the recommendations\n\n| # | Task | Effort | Value |\n|---|------|--------|-------|\n| 4 | Split Scheduler page (559 lines) into sub-components | Medium | Already has JobsTab/ErrorsTab inside, page itself is ~280 lines. Not urgent. |\n| 7 | Backfill Memory page content | Low | Already reads real files — the 11 daily logs exist. Content is sparse (system health logs). Would need to write richer summaries. |\n| 11 | Dark/light theme toggle | Medium | Would require adding OKLCH light variants for all components. Nice-to-have. |\n\nEverything else is done. The Scheduler split (#4) is the only medium-effort item remaining — and honestly it's already partially decomposed internally. And the Memory content (#7) would need you to provide richer source material since the daily logs are mostly auto-generated health checks.\n\n**My recommendation:** Ship what's done. The Scheduler page works fine at 559 lines. The Memory page shows real data now. A theme toggle is a feature request, not a bug fix.\n\nWant me to push the latest commits or is there anything else you'd like tackled?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/owl-alpha","usage":{"input":15613,"output":503,"cacheRead":134016,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":150132,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779963989416,"responseId":"gen-1779963989-YNTVvEB1n2ECNpY6Tgzz"}}
