{"type":"message","id":"a30d0011","parentId":"bb464699","timestamp":"2026-05-28T11:42:20.951Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The earlier Aider Integration section is now redundant with the new Build Tool Rules section. Let me replace it:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"cc8db7be-cfba-4e2d-a142-82af6f31bce3","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/Users/spacemonkey/.openclaw/workspace/FRAMEWORK.md","edits":[{"oldText":"## Aider Integration\n\n**When to use Aider:**\n- Large multi-file refactors too complex for direct `edit`/`write` tools\n- Splitting modules, renaming across codebase, bulk import restructuring\n- Always use non-interactive mode: `aider --message \"...\" --yes`\n\n**When NOT to use Aider:**\n- Quick single-file fixes — use direct `edit`/`write`\n- Tasks requiring browser/visual verification\n- Anything that needs interactive debugging\n\n**Configuration:**\n- Installed: `pip install aider-chat` (v0.82.3 installed)\n- API key: `OPENROUTER_API_KEY` (already configured)\n- Model: `openrouter/openrouter/owl-alpha`\n- Config: `~/.aider.conf.yml`\n- Usage: `cd <project> && python3 -m aider --model openrouter/openrouter/owl-alpha --no-auto-commits --yes --dark-mode --message \"refactor X across Y files\"\n- Never use interactive TUI / tmux sessions — non-interactive `--message` only\n- Set `--no-auto-commits` to maintain our own git workflow","newText":"## Aider Configuration\n\n- Installed: `pip install aider-chat` (v0.82.3) with OpenRouter API key\n- Model: `openrouter/openrouter/owl-alpha`\n- Config: `~/.aider.conf.yml`\n- **Usage:** `cd <project> && python3 -m aider --model openrouter/openrouter/owl-alpha --no-auto-commits --yes --dark-mode --message \"...\"`\n- `--no-auto-commits` to maintain our own git workflow\n- Never use interactive TUI / tmux — `--message` with `--yes` only\n\nSee **Build Tool Rules** above for when to use Aider vs direct edits vs sub-agents."}]},"partialArgs":"{\"path\": \"/Users/spacemonkey/.openclaw/workspace/FRAMEWORK.md\", \"edits\": [{\"oldText\": \"## Aider Integration\\n\\n**When to use Aider:**\\n- Large multi-file refactors too complex for direct `edit`/`write` tools\\n- Splitting modules, renaming across codebase, bulk import restructuring\\n- Always use non-interactive mode: `aider --message \\\"...\\\" --yes`\\n\\n**When NOT to use Aider:**\\n- Quick single-file fixes — use direct `edit`/`write`\\n- Tasks requiring browser/visual verification\\n- Anything that needs interactive debugging\\n\\n**Configuration:**\\n- Installed: `pip install aider-chat` (v0.82.3 installed)\\n- API key: `OPENROUTER_API_KEY` (already configured)\\n- Model: `openrouter/openrouter/owl-alpha`\\n- Config: `~/.aider.conf.yml`\\n- Usage: `cd <project> && python3 -m aider --model openrouter/openrouter/owl-alpha --no-auto-commits --yes --dark-mode --message \\\"refactor X across Y files\\\"\\n- Never use interactive TUI / tmux sessions — non-interactive `--message` only\\n- Set `--no-auto-commits` to maintain our own git workflow\", \"newText\": \"## Aider Configuration\\n\\n- Installed: `pip install aider-chat` (v0.82.3) with OpenRouter API key\\n- Model: `openrouter/openrouter/owl-alpha`\\n- Config: `~/.aider.conf.yml`\\n- **Usage:** `cd <project> && python3 -m aider --model openrouter/openrouter/owl-alpha --no-auto-commits --yes --dark-mode --message \\\"...\\\"`\\n- `--no-auto-commits` to maintain our own git workflow\\n- Never use interactive TUI / tmux — `--message` with `--yes` only\\n\\nSee **Build Tool Rules** above for when to use Aider vs direct edits vs sub-agents.\"}]}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/owl-alpha","usage":{"input":477,"output":468,"cacheRead":161536,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":162481,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779965338373,"responseId":"gen-1779965338-ymoQWlGsKc10Gqv4puL3"}}
