re the daily memory logs included?\n\n═══════════════════════════════\n4. DISASTER RECOVERY GAP ANALYSIS\n═══════════════════════════════\n\nIf my Mac mini died tomorrow and I had to restore to a new machine:\n\n- What would I lose? (anything NOT backed up)\n- What would I need to manually recreate? (API keys, configs,\n LaunchAgents, cron jobs)\n- Is there a RECOVERY_GUIDE.md? Is it up to date?\n- Could I actually restore from the WD MyCloud backup, or is it\n just files with no restore procedure?\n\n═══════════════════════════════\n5. REPORT\n═══════════════════════════════\n\nGive me an honest assessment:\n- Is our backup situation healthy or are we one disk failure\n away from losing everything?\n- What's the single biggest gap?\n- What's the one thing I should fix today?"}],"timestamp":1779966780482}}
