{"type":"message","id":"b916372f","parentId":"11fe8c10","timestamp":"2026-05-28T11:53:24.526Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The WD MyCloud **is** mounted at `/Volumes/WD-MyCloud/` and it already has the `OpenClaw/` directory with `backups/`, `logs/`, `sync/`, etc. The symlink at `/Volumes/OpenClaw-WD/openclaw-agent-backup` → `/Volumes/WD-MyCloud` confirms this. Let me check if it's writable:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"ac25b2f9-5b12-4559-8141-edb5e4016522","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Check if WD-MyCloud is writable\ntouch /Volumes/WD-MyCloud/OpenClaw/.write-test 2>&1 && echo \"WRITABLE\" && rm /Volumes/WD-MyCloud/OpenClaw/.write-test || echo \"NOT WRITABLE\"\necho \"===\"\n# Check existing backup contents\nls -laR /Volumes/WD-MyCloud/OpenClaw/backups/ 2>/dev/null\necho \"===\"\nls -la /Volumes/WD-MyCloud/OpenClaw/logs/ 2>/dev/null\necho \"===\"\ncat /Volumes/WD-MyCloud/OpenClaw/logs/backup.log 2>/dev/null || echo \"No backup.log\"\necho \"===\"\ncat /Volumes/WD-MyCloud/OpenClaw/README.txt 2>/dev/null","timeout":10},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"# Check if WD-MyCloud is writable\\ntouch /Volumes/WD-MyCloud/OpenClaw/.write-test 2>&1 && echo \\\"WRITABLE\\\" && rm /Volumes/WD-MyCloud/OpenClaw/.write-test || echo \\\"NOT WRITABLE\\\"\\necho \\\"===\\\"\\n# Check existing backup contents\\nls -laR /Volumes/WD-MyCloud/OpenClaw/backups/ 2>/dev/null\\necho \\\"===\\\"\\nls -la /Volumes/WD-MyCloud/OpenClaw/logs/ 2>/dev/null\\necho \\\"===\\\"\\ncat /Volumes/WD-MyCloud/OpenClaw/logs/backup.log 2>/dev/null || echo \\\"No backup.log\\\"\\necho \\\"===\\\"\\ncat /Volumes/WD-MyCloud/OpenClaw/README.txt 2>/dev/null\", \"timeout\": 10}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/owl-alpha","usage":{"input":874,"output":282,"cacheRead":44800,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45956,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779969182573,"responseId":"