s/daily/ or backups/weekly/\n2. Extract with: tar -xzf backup-file.tar.gz -C ~\n3. Verify with: openclaw agents list\n\nQuestions? See: ~/.openclaw/workspace/BACKUP_GUIDE.md","cwd":"/Users/spacemonkey/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1779969204579}}
